Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,主呀 给我们力量来坚守\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Give us strength, O Lord, to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:54.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是上帝手中 卑微的罪人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We recognize that we are poor sinners in the hands of an angry God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,请以手包围我们 守护我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let the circle be unbroken until the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿们 - 阿们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Amen. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢各位\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:17.49,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谣言管制会议 以下是案情\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is Rumor Control. Here are the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}As some of you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一架337型号紧急逃生艇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}a 337 model EEV crash-landed here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,在早上六点坠落此地\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}at 0600 on the morning watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:33.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有一名生还者 两具尸体\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There was one survivor, two dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,以及损毁得 无法维修的生化人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and a droid that was hopelessly smashed beyond repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,生还者是个女人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The survivor is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Is she pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:47.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说我已经发誓 要终生禁欲\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I just want to say that I've taken a vow of celibacy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,包括对女人在内\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}that also includes women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们全都发过誓 - 闭上你的臭嘴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- We've all taken the vow! - Shut your gob, Morse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢公司政策\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I do not appreciate company policy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让她和囚犯及狱卒 混在一起\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}allowing her to freely intermingle with inmates and the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:03.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这位兄弟想说的是 任何外人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Our brother means to say we view the presence of any outsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是一个女人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}especially a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:10.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,都会破坏这里 和谐统一的精神\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}as a violation of the harmony, a potential break in the spiritual unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道 大家的想法\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We are aware of your feelings in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:17.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我已申请救援小组前来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You will be pleased to know that I have requested a rescue team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:24.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,若无阻碍 一周内将到达 然后尽快将她带离此地\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hopefully they will be here inside of a week and evacuate her ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,少来这一套\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Don't give us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她的身体状况如何？ - 伤势不重\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's her medical status? - She doesn't seem too badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:34.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,目前昏迷中 未能做更精确诊断\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}She's unconscious. Can't give you a more specific diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她能活下来吗？ - 我想应该会\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Will she live? - I would think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:42.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不希望那女人 在救援小组到达前\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's in everybody's interest she doesn't come out of the infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:47.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,离开医疗室 没人伴随更不可以 对吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}until the rescue team arrives, and certainly not without an escort, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:56.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我们必须坚守 日常生活 不要过度激动\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Gentlemen! We should all stick to our set routine and not get unduly agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Correct? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 谢谢大家\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们最好早点到 否则她就死定了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Better get here soon or there ain't gonna be much left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己调的鸡尾酒 给你前所未有的感受\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Just a little cocktail of my own mix. Sort of an eye-opener.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是医生？ - 我叫克里蒙斯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You a doctor? - My name is Clemens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这里的医疗主任 - 这里？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm the Chief Medical Officer here. - Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,复仇161星\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fury 161.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:10.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,银河系最偏远的劳动监狱 一提起就令我伤心\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's one of Weyland-Yutani's backwater work prisons, it grieves me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:18.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是镇静剂\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is basically a stabilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:24.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我得剃掉你的头发 这里的头虱很多\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I really ought to shave your head. We have a big problem with lice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你剪发 你自己剪耻毛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When you feel better I'll give you some clippers for your private parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么来的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你乘坐的逃生艇坠毁\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You crash-landed in an EEV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,进入大气层前 才脱离你的母船\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Separated from your mother ship before you hit our atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,知道你长眠多久吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Any idea how long you were in hypersleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然苏醒 可能对身体有影响\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Coming out the way you did can jolt your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会病几个星期 - 没错\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'll be sick for a couple of weeks. - Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 其他人呢？ - 全死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Where are the others? - They didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？ - 无一幸存\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What? - They didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我要到船上\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have to get to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你现在还不能去 - 给我穿衣服\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You're in no condition for that. - Wanna get me some clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你要我这样出去？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}or should I go like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:18.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到本地居民的性情 我建议你穿衣服\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Given the nature of our indigenous population, I would suggest clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好久没见过女色\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}None of them has seen a woman in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Neither have I, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里曾经收容五千名囚犯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This used to be a 5,000-convict facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:36.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在却只有25名\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}but it's been reduced to a custodial staff of 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么？ - 保持火焰不熄\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Why? - To keep the pilot light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,什么火焰？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pilot light for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,封闭式熔炉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Blast furnace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,天然沼气 我们有个铸造厂 蕾普莉中尉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Natural methane. We have a foundry, Lt Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯打造铅片 围堵有毒废物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The inmates forge lead sheets for toxic waste containment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我的名字？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就写在你短裤背面\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's stenciled on the back of your shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把铁缆松开\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Release the cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 尸体在哪里？ - 在殓房\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Where are the bodies? - We have a morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:35.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,调查小组一个星期后到达\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We put them there until the investigative team arrives - in about a week, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:39.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有一名生化人 - 残缺不全\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- There was a droid. - Disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:43.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是碎片 我们把残骸丢到垃圾场\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There were bits and pieces everywhere. We put what was left on the rubbish tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那名下士 被安全支架刺死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The corporal was impaled by that safety support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,死得不明不白\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Never knew what hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她…溺死在低温舱内\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}She... drowned in her cryo-tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:59.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她没有知觉… 当她死去时\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't think she was conscious... when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了？ - 她在哪里？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's the matter? - Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,在停尸间\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:31.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我要看她\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我要看看她的遗体\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have to see what's left of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:42.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你这么坚持？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Is there any particular reason that you're so insistent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:46.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我要确定她的死因\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yes. I have to be sure how she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对这种事情 实在不必罗唆\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I hate to be repetitious about such a sensitive subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,但她很明显是溺死的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}but it is perfectly clear that she drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她是你女儿吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Was she your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No. She wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我独处一下 好吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Could I have a moment alone, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:54.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她在干嘛？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们得验尸 - 什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- We have to do an autopsy. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 我们得查清楚她的死因\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I told you. We have to make sure how she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:22.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 她是溺死的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I told you... she drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢肯定\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得看看她的体内\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have to see inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:32.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你精神恍惚 - 我有很好的理由\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You're disorientated. - I have a very, very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:36.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那就请你把理由告诉我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Perhaps you'd like to share that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她很可能受到感染\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Possible contagion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,哪种感染？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What kind, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 霍乱 - 霍乱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Cholera. - Cholera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:55.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,两百年来 一宗霍乱病例都没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There hasn't been a case of cholera reported for 200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Everything's in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:45.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有感染的迹象 没有疾病的征状\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's no sign of infection. No indication of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,胸腔 打开胸腔\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Her chest. Open her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.84,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:34.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,肺部\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Lungs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,充满液体\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}flooded with fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她是溺死的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ergo, she drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是白痴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now, since I'm not a complete idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:56.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 你到底在找什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}would you like to tell me what we're really looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:09.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 克先生 - 狱长\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Mr. Clemens. - Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:15.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没见过蕾普莉中尉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't believe you've met Lieutenant Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:19.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是怎么回事 克先生？ - 是的 长官 怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's going on, Mr. Clemens? - That's right, sir. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:27.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴蕾普莉中尉 已经觉得好很多\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}First, the lieutenant is feeling much better, I'm happy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:31.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,另外 基於公共卫生 我正在验尸\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Second, in the interest of public health, I am performing an autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有我的同意？ - 我来不及向你请示\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Without my authority. - There didn't seem to be time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:39.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,结果一切无碍 没有感染\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But it's turned out all right. There's no sign of contagion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:44.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 蕾中尉最好 别在囚犯面前走动\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Good. But it might be helpful if Ripley didn't parade around in front of the prisoners,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,听说她已经这么做过\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}as I am told she did in the last hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:51.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她的状况若有变化 你也要让我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It might also be helpful if you informed me of any change in her physical status.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这要求过分吗？ - 尸体必须火葬\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Or would that be asking too much? - We have to cremate the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:23:00.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯 我们要保存尸体 直到救援小组到达\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nonsense. We'll keep the bodies on ice till the rescue team arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:01.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,冷藏保存\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}On ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:04.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这会影响公共卫生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There is the public-health issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:10.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾中尉认为目前 仍有传染病存在的可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The lieutenant feels there is still the possibility of a communicable infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:16.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不是说没有疾病征状？ - 这孩子看来是溺死的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You said there was no sign of disease. - It would appear that the child drowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:20.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不过未经化验 是不可能完全确定的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}but without proper laboratory tests it's impossible to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:26.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为不该忽视 感染病毒的可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I would consider it unwise to tolerate even the possibility of an unwelcome virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:32.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要是霍乱突然蔓延 你一定会面目无光\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}An outbreak of... cholera would look extremely bad on a report, would it not, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:37.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这所监狱的25名囚犯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've 25 prisoners in this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:39.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,全都有双Y染色体\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All double-Y chromos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:43.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,全是小偷、强奸犯、杀人犯 全都是人渣\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All thieves, rapists, murderers, child molesters... All scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:48.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们信教 并不代表他们很安全\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Just because they've taken on religion doesn't make them any less dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不干涉他们的信仰\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I try not to offend their convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:53.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,也不想扰乱这里的秩序\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't want to upset the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:57.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想引发风波\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't want ripples in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:02.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不让女人勾起他们的邪念\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I don't want a woman walking around, giving them ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:06.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 为我自身安全着想\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I see. For my own personal safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没错\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:14.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我把火葬的事交给你 克先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I will leave the details of the cremation to you, Mr. Clemens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:20.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可以用熔炉 不过十点以前要回牢房\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They may use the furnace, but I want everyone back in lockup by 2200 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:51.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节提早到来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Our Christmas has come early.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.28,0:24:54.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么意思？ - 有死牛就是好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What do you mean? - Any dead oxes are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.95,0:24:58.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,满身跳蚤的臭东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Smelly bastards all covered in lice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.41,0:25:02.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只剩下七只 就算处理完了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's only seven of the friggin' things left, then we're done with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:04.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌冲洗这臭东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I hate hosin' these bastards down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:07.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,每次搞得我浑身是粪\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Always get shite all over me boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.04,0:25:11.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对了 法兰克 - 怎么了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Talking of hosing things down, Frank... - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.09,0:25:13.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有机会的话 你想跟她说什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If you had the chance, what would you say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.97,0:25:17.47,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么意思？ - 你知道的 有机会的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What do you mean? - You know, if you got the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.55,0:25:20.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是说平常的时候吗？ - 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You mean, casual, like? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要是在饭堂遇到 你会说什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How would you put it to her if you bumped into her in the mess hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.98,0:25:26.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.90,0:25:29.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我对女人很有办法\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I've never had any problem with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.65,0:25:32.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我会说"午安 亲爱的 好吗？"\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'd say "Good day, my dear. How's it going?"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.53,0:25:35.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,"我可以帮你做什么吗？"\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}"Anything I can do to be of service?"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.32,0:25:38.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,然后看着她 从上看到下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then I'd give her the look, up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.41,0:25:41.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,然后眨眼睛 色迷迷的笑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then I'd give her the wink. A dirty smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.87,0:25:44.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她就会明白 - 是的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- She'd soon get the picture. - Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.37,0:25:48.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她就会说 “来亲我吧 老色鬼”\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then she'd say "Kiss my arse, you horny old bugger."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:53.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我会去亲她 浑身上下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'd be happy to kiss her arse. I'd be happy to kiss her anywhere she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.09,0:25:57.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 但要粗暴点 激烈点 明白吗？法兰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah, but treat 'em mean, keep 'em keen. Right, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.68,0:26:02.55,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你 把女王当妓女 把妓女当是女王\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Told you before, Murph. Treat a queen like a whore and a whore like a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:05.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You can't go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.94,0:26:09.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是怎么死的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What do you think killed Babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.31,0:26:11.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 反正已归西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Beats me. She just keeled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:16.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她多大？ - 11岁吧 正值青春\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How old was she? - Guards say 11. In her prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.32,0:26:22.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 等一下切碎了 一样要丢进炉里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Never mind. We'll chop her up later and throw her in the stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:24.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.79,0:26:27.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,法兰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.83,0:26:31.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.90,0:27:39.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子和这男人 已离开我们的世界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We commit this child and this man to your keeping, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:47.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已远离黑暗\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Their bodies have been taken from the shadow of our nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.33,0:27:53.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们获得解脱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They have been released
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.38,0:27:57.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,远离黑暗与痛苦\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}from all darkness and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:05.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子和这男人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The child and the man
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.89,0:28:08.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,已离开我们的世界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}have gone beyond our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.85,0:28:13.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已达到永恒\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They are forever eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.73,0:28:15.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,永垂不朽\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and everlasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.20,0:28:25.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,尘归尘\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ashes to ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.78,0:28:28.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,土归土\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}dust to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:31.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.54,0:28:36.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么无辜者受到惩罚？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why are the innocent punished?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.76,0:28:43.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么必须牺牲？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why the sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.43,0:28:49.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有痛苦？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.98,0:28:54.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,世间原无承诺\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There aren't any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.06,0:28:58.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,世事无常\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nothing's certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.11,0:29:04.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,少数人能蒙主宠召 得到拯救\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Only that some get called, some get saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.32,0:29:10.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会了解我们留在人世 必须面对的困苦和伤痛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}She won't ever know the hardship and grief for those of us left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.91,0:29:15.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将遗体交托于虚无\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We commit these bodies to the void...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.29,0:29:18.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,并且满心欢喜\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}with a glad heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:33.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,因为每一颗种子 必将长出花朵\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}For within each seed, there is a promise of a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.06,0:29:42.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,每次死亡 无论多么微不足道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And within each death, no matter how small,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.07,0:29:46.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一个新生命\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}there's always a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.28,0:29:53.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一个新的开始\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}A new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.29,0:29:58.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,阿们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:02.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,阿们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.20,0:30:40.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 唯一生还者是女人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I tell ya, it's fuckin' weird. The only one that survived that crash is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.81,0:31:40.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.11,0:31:47.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很多谣言说这里不很和谐\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's a lot of talk going around that we've got some disharmony here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.15,0:31:50.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我是什么问题吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Any of you guys wanna tell me what the problem is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.37,0:31:56.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 兄弟\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on. Speak to me, brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.04,0:32:00.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All right, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:04.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕黑暗和虫子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't mind the dark. I don't mind the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:10.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,也不怕每周一次 走进又湿又冷的隧道中\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't mind wandering around in some cold, wet, damp tunnel for a week at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:12.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,但我讨厌葛立\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But I mind Golic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:18.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是这样吗？ - 对 他又臭又疯疯癫癫\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- That the way you feel about it? - Yeah. The guy's crazy and he smells bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.85,0:32:22.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再和他一起出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I ain't going out with him any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.27,0:32:29.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么话要说？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You got anything to say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.57,0:32:36.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是得跟着你们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The boy's going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.24,0:32:41.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,葛立只是个可怜的废人 和你我没有不同\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Golic is just another poor, miserable, suffering son of a bitch, just like you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.25,0:32:43.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他很臭 - 还疯疯癫癫\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- He smells worse. - And he's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.50,0:32:45.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我来这套\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Knock off the shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.05,0:32:50.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有事要做\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You've got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.21,0:32:53.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再听到 任何有关葛立的事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't wanna hear another word about Golic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:32:57.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.20,0:34:01.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦先生 如我所想\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}As I thought, Mr. Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:04.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如你所想 - 你作主吧 长官\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- As I thought. - You called it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.42,0:34:15.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想 谢谢你在葬体说的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I just wanted to... say thanks for what you said at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.51,0:34:23.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的朋友一定会很感激… - 你不会想认识我 小姐\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- My friends would've appreciated... - You don't wanna know me, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.23,0:34:27.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是专杀女人的强奸犯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm a murderer and rapist of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.48,0:34:31.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.82,0:34:37.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜我一定令你很紧张\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I guess I must make you nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.00,0:34:56.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有任何信仰吗 妹子？ - 谈不上\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Do you have any faith, sister? - Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.30,0:34:58.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很足够的信仰\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've got a lot of faith here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.72,0:35:02.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至足够让你加入\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Enough even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:07.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以为女人不准加入 - 以前从未有过女人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I thought women weren't allowed. - Well, we've never had any before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.27,0:35:11.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们容忍任何人 甚至令人无法容忍的人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But we tolerate anybody. Even the intolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.98,0:35:15.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.82,0:35:19.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是原则 不是针对你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's just a statement of principle, nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:22.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等待最好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You see, we've got a good place to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.95,0:35:26.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在…没有任何诱惑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And until now... no temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.75,0:35:33.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在等什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.06,0:35:48.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,等上帝回来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We're waiting for God to return
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:51.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,救赎我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and raise his servants to redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.27,0:35:58.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,五年前迪伦和其他人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Dillon and the rest of the alternative people
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.28,0:36:02.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,接受宗教信仰\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}embraced religion, as it were, about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,再喝一杯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Tincture?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.74,0:36:07.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我正在服药 - 不见得吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm on medication. - Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.33,0:36:10.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪一种宗教？ - 某种相信千年末世的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What kind of religion? - Some sort of apocalyptic,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.87,0:36:14.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,基督教原教旨主义派\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}millenarian, Christian fundamentalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.34,0:36:16.49,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对 - 正是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Right. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.59,0:36:19.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是公司想关闭监狱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When the company wanted to close the facility down,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.76,0:36:23.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,迪伦和其他人希望留下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Dillon and the rest of the converts wanted to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.47,0:36:27.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们获准以守卫身份留下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And they were allowed to remain as custodians,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.43,0:36:32.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,加上两名管理员和 一名医疗主任\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}with two minders and a medical officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.19,0:36:35.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.61,0:36:39.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么得到这么好的差事？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How did you get this wonderful assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:44.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这新发型吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How do you like your new haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.78,0:36:46.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还算好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.93,0:37:07.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了你 得罪安德鲁\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now that I've gone out on a limb for you with Andrews,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.72,0:37:11.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那好人的关系 现在更加恶化\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}damaged my already less-than-perfect relationship with that good man,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.93,0:37:16.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我也向你说过 复仇161星的无聊历史\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and briefed you on the humdrum history of Fury 161,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.07,0:37:19.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可否告诉我 在女孩体内找什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}can you not tell me what you were looking for in the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.07,0:37:22.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我有吸引力吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Are you attracted to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.95,0:37:26.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一方面？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.37,0:37:30.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,“那”方面\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:33.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你很直接\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're very direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.17,0:37:38.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我流浪了很久\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I've been out here a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.71,0:37:41.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.18,0:37:51.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  In the year 7510
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.68,0:37:53.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  If God's a-comin'
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.93,0:37:57.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  He oughta make it by then
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.69,0:38:01.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  Maybe he'll look around and say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.36,0:38:04.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  Guess it's time for the Judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.56,0:38:34.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,∮  In the year
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.74,0:38:42.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 史派克\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hey, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.25,0:38:52.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你在下面吗？在做什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Are you down there? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.08,0:39:40.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙你垂青我真的很感激\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I really appreciate your affections.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.21,0:39:44.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,但我注意到 你回避我的问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But I am aware that they deflected my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.59,0:39:49.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,当然你用的方法很巧妙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In the nicest possible way, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.43,0:39:56.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你真扫兴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're spoiling the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.14,0:40:02.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我得尽我的职责 我只想知道为何要火葬\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have a job to do. I just want to know why we had to cremate the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.11,0:40:07.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为既然上了你的床 就应该回答你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And now that I'm in your cot, you think I owe you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.86,0:40:13.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你得给我一个理由 但这与上不上床无关\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I think you owe me an answer. Being in my bed's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.12,0:40:24.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我在长眠期间发了可怕的梦 我得知道是什么害死她\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I had a terrible dream in hypersleep, and I had to be sure what killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.29,0:40:26.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能错了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Anyway, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:31.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.97,0:40:34.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我又犯了错\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And now I've made another mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:38.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的？什么错？ - 和囚犯搞关系\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Really? What's that? - Fraternizing with a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.47,0:40:42.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,肉体接触 这触犯规律 对吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Physical contact. It's against the rules, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.10,0:40:45.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.90,0:40:49.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 几时发生的？ - 你应该很清楚\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- When was this? - I think you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.66,0:40:56.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是囚犯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm not a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.66,0:41:02.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你脑后有一个电脑条码\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You have a bar code on the back of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.96,0:41:08.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那的确应该解释\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That does deserve an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.72,0:41:13.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在还未到时候\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But I don't think now is the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.68,0:41:20.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我令你觉得扫兴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry. We are rather spoiling things, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.39,0:41:25.47,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,克先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Mr. Clemens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:27.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Mr. Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.77,0:41:32.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,狱长安德鲁 要你马上到22号通风孔\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Superintendent Andrews would like you to report to vent shaft 22. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.32,0:41:35.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 发生了意外 - 严重吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- We've had an accident. - Something serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.49,0:41:40.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说 有一名囚犯…被切碎了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You could call it that. One of our prisoners has been... diced.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.91,0:41:43.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 得走了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:49.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有职务在身\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Official duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.45,0:42:22.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 墨菲 - 你怎么知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Murphy. - How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.38,0:42:26.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的靴子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's his boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.09,0:42:30.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是我派他来的 他是个笨蛋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I gave him the assignment, sir. He was a wanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.10,0:42:33.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别自责 亚伦先生 不是你的错\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No apologies, Mr. Aaron. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.32,0:42:48.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好说的 他当场死亡\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Well, not much to say, is there? Death was instantaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.57,0:42:49.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.70,0:42:52.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他被吸入风扇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I take it he was pulled into the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:56.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 突然而来的一阵风 - 对 我也差点被卷进风扇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Rush of air, I'd imagine. Except... - Right! Almost happened to me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.41,0:43:01.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过多少次离风扇远点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I've told them so many times: Stay away from the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.29,0:43:04.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有人肯听 - 除了风扇一直吹着\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Nobody bloody listens. - Except the fan was blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.93,0:43:14.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么？ - 不知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's that? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.06,0:43:19.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,半小时后来见我 克先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I want to see you in my quarters in 30 minutes, if you please, Mr. Clemens.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.16,0:44:15.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.24,0:44:20.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人到处乱走 会气死安德鲁\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Wandering around without an escort will really piss Superintendent Andrews off.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.00,0:44:25.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那件意外是怎么回事？ - 一名囚犯死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Tell me about your accident. - One of the prisoners has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:29.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？怎么死的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Really? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.51,0:44:31.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,在通风孔\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In the air shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.84,0:44:34.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的家伙 掉进9尺长的风扇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Poor sod backed into a nine-foot fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.68,0:44:41.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我在离现场不远 发现一样东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I found something at the accident site. Just a bit away from where it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.69,0:44:44.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一个印痕 烧过的痕迹\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}A mark. A burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.75,0:44:52.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在那女孩的低温舱 所发现的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Like the one you found on the girl's cryo-tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.02,0:44:59.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我跟你同一阵线\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Look, I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.06,0:45:03.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮你 但我要知道这是怎么回事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I want to help, but I need to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.57,0:45:06.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,或是 你认为这是怎么回事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Or what you think is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.65,0:45:12.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,若你想帮我 就找一部语音电脑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If you really wanna help, find me a computer with audio capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.78,0:45:14.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我解读航行记录器\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}so I can access this flight recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.95,0:45:18.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有那种设备\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We don't have anything like that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.16,0:45:19.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 主教呢？ - 主教？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What about Bishop? - Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.87,0:45:22.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起坠机的生化人？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The droid that crashed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:24.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能指给你看\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I can point you in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.84,0:45:28.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不能陪你去 我和别人有约\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I can't join you. I have a previous engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.59,0:45:35.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来了 葛立 不要乱弄\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This looks off. Golic, don't fidget.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.72,0:45:38.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's all this shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.39,0:45:40.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有包好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's not properly wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.69,0:45:44.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他笨头笨脑 - 只会吃\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What the hell's he ever do right? - Eat. He does that pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.19,0:45:47.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,葛立 你为墨菲点枝蜡烛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Golic. You light a candle for Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.57,0:45:49.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我会点很多支\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'll light a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.78,0:45:56.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他真好 从未抱怨过\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He was special. Never complained about me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.87,0:45:59.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢他\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.59,0:46:05.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那样吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Is it true what they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.59,0:46:08.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他的头被打碎了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}His head split into 100 pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.10,0:46:10.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谁有火柴？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK, who's got the matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.56,0:46:17.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 克先生 请坐 - 谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Sit down, Mr. Clemens. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.73,0:46:22.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 加糖？ - 不用\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Sugar? - No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.61,0:46:25.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 加奶？ - 一点点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Milk? - Just a little, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.87,0:46:30.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 亚伦先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thank you, Mr. Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.09,0:46:45.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,给我听好 你这浑蛋 你再耍我 我就斩开你两半\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Listen to me, you piece of shit! Screw with me one more time, I'll cut you in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.93,0:46:49.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我听不懂\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm sorry, I don't think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.26,0:46:52.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,七点我接到总公司的消息\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}At 0700 hours I received word from the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:54.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知 那是这儿…\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is the first high-level communication
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.98,0:46:59.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,收到的第一份高阶层讯息\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}this installation has ever received, to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.65,0:47:03.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要我们看牢这女人 她是最高优先考虑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They want this woman looked after. They consider her to be high priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.78,0:47:06.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么？ - 我也不知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Why? - I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.86,0:47:09.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何让她离开医疗室？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why did you let her out of the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.91,0:47:12.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,墨菲发生意外 是因为\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This accident with Murphy is what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.50,0:47:15.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你让人满脑子歪念乱跑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}when one of these dumb sons of bitches gets a hard-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.41,0:47:18.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是医生 你是狱卒\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm a doctor, you're the jailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.67,0:47:22.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道你的真面目\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We both know exactly what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.38,0:47:24.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.67,0:47:30.55,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我最好离开 在你身边令我非常不愉快\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I think it might be better if I left. I find you unpleasant to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.64,0:47:33.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？你要想想 克先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Isn't that lovely! Consider this, Mr. Clemens.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.06,0:47:39.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我把你的臭史 告诉你的新朋友吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How would you like me to explain your sordid history to your new-found friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.48,0:47:43.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为了她个人的想法\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}For her personal edification, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.28,0:47:45.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now sit the hell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.75,0:48:02.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你 你喜怒无常 傲慢无理 也可能很危险\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't like you. You're unpredictable, insolent, possibly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.67,0:48:05.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你对任何事都有疑问\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You question everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.51,0:48:10.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这里不需要医疗主任 我马上要你滚蛋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If I didn't need a medical officer, I wouldn't let you within light years of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.59,0:48:13.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我感激不尽 - 少讲风凉话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm eternally grateful. - Keep your sarcasms to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.63,0:48:17.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在…我该知道什么事？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now, is there anything I should know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.90,0:48:22.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 关于什么？ - 那女人 少骗我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- About what? - About the woman. Don't play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.98,0:48:25.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你几乎随时在她旁边\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You spend every second you can with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.44,0:48:30.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才相信你是为了治疗\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I have my suspicions that not all of your concerns with her are medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.28,0:48:35.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她跟你说过什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Has she said anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.62,0:48:40.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她从哪里来？有什么任务？ 为什么会在逃生艇内？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}About where she's from, what her mission is? What she was doing in an EEV?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.46,0:48:43.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她说她们打了败仗\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}She said she was part of a combat unit that came to grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.46,0:48:46.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想其他都是机密\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Beyond that, I assume it's all classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.59,0:48:49.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我没再给她压力\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I haven't pressed her for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.43,0:48:51.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就这样？真的吗？ - 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- That's all? - That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.84,0:48:53.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你确定 - 是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You sure? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.76,0:48:56.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有了 - 没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Nothing more? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.56,0:49:02.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.30,0:50:54.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你这个婊子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shut up, you fuckin' bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.63,0:50:56.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 婊子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shut up, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.09,0:51:00.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.51,0:51:03.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你的 - 不要动\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Fuck you! No! - Hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.31,0:51:07.26,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.11,0:51:17.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.07,0:51:22.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你这王八蛋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.79,0:51:32.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 我得重新教育几位弟兄\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Take off. I gotta re-educate some of the brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.71,0:51:34.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谈一下心灵改革的问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've gotta discuss some matters of the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.79,0:51:48.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,香烟\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.43,0:52:07.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,干吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.23,0:52:16.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有十条街这么长\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is like ten city blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.03,0:52:22.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有多少？ - 这是第176个\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How many? - This makes 176.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.75,0:52:30.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,吃东西小声点 我正在算这区段有多大\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Can't you chew any quieter? I'm trying to figure how big this compartment is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.09,0:52:34.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这么吵我无法思考 - 别说脏话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I can't think with this goddamn noise... - You're not supposed to swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.09,0:52:35.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.34,0:52:39.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们绕行过整个区段\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've encircled this entire compartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.56,0:52:41.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿！ - 干嘛？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Hey! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.65,0:52:49.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么狗屁玩意？ - 说脏话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What the shit is doing that? - Swearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.52,0:52:53.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 说狗屁没关系 我又没骂上帝\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shut up! It's all right to say "shit". It ain't against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.11,0:52:56.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,蜡烛怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's going on with the candles?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.33,0:53:06.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是附近通风孔 吹来的逆风\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Must be the wind from one of the vent shafts. Backwash from the closest circulating unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.08,0:53:08.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要是蜡烛都被吹熄 我们怎么知道位置？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If all the candles go out, how do we know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.04,0:53:12.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只好派人回去 重新点亮\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Somebody will have to go back and relight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.63,0:53:15.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I guess I'm nominated.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.60,0:53:27.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 兄弟\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Watch your step, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.99,0:53:40.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 谁在开玩笑？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK, who are the comedians?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.11,0:54:19.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.24,0:54:24.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.12,0:54:29.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快 抓住\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Quick, in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.21,0:54:30.49,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,救我 救我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Help me, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.00,0:54:35.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,走！快走！\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Go! Fuckin' go!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.21,0:54:40.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,走 走 快点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Go on! Go on! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:52.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,拿来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.98,0:55:36.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把这臭东西弄掉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get this fuckin' thing off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.61,0:55:38.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.42,0:56:37.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.84,0:56:43.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 蕾普莉 - 嗨 主教\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Hello, Ripley. - Hello, Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.01,0:56:47.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你感觉如何？ - 我的腿很痛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How are you feeling? - My legs hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.89,0:56:53.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我很难过 - 没关系 我只是个烤面包机\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm sorry. - That's OK. I'm just a glorified toaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.64,0:56:56.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗？ 我喜欢你的新发型\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How are you? I like your new haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.95,0:57:01.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能查出航行记录器资料？ - 没问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Can you access data on the flight recorder? - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.90,0:57:30.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,葛立\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Golic?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.03,0:57:37.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.03,0:57:41.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,苏拉可号发生什么事？ 低温舱为何弹射出来？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What happened on the Sulaco? Why were our cryo-tubes ejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.08,0:57:44.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,静态平衡受干扰\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Stasis interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.71,0:57:50.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,低温舱起火 重覆 低温舱…\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fire in cryogenic compartment. Repeat: Fire in cryogenic...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.21,0:57:55.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？怎么起火的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What happened? What started the fire, Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.13,0:57:58.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你听得到吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.09,0:58:03.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,电线短路 地板的材料烧起来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The fire was electrical. It was in the subflooring.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.60,0:58:07.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,救生船脱离母舰前 有没有东西在舰上？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Did the sensors pick up anything moving around prior to separation?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.81,0:58:10.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿好暗 蕾普莉 我的视力大不如前\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's very dark here. I'm not what I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.86,0:58:14.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 记录器有没有显示？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Just tell me. Does the recorder indicate anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.03,0:58:17.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,舰上有没有异形？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Was there an alien on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.24,0:58:21.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.20,0:58:28.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它还在苏拉可号 还是和我们一起坠机？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Is it on the Sulaco or did it come with us in the EEV?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.29,0:58:31.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它一直都和我们一起\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It was with us all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.85,0:58:49.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,公司知不知道？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Does the company know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.02,0:58:53.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,公司知道舰上的每一件事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The company knows everything that happened on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.44,0:58:57.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都输入电脑 传回总公司\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It all goes into the computer and gets sent back to network.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.49,0:58:59.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还是要异形\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And they want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.92,0:59:03.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,帮个忙 切断电源\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I hurt. Do me a favor. Disconnect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.89,0:59:09.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我被修好 也无法回复正常\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I could be reworked. But I'll never be top-of-the-line again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.22,0:59:12.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿消失\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'd rather be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.81,0:59:16.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.36,0:59:18.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就当为我好吧 蕾普莉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do it for me, Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.96,0:59:37.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 不是我干的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It wasn't me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.13,0:59:41.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那一条龙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Help me. It was the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.34,0:59:44.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,吸食人的心灵 谁也无法阻挡\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Feeds on minds. Nobody can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.80,0:59:48.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伯格和雷恩呢？ - 全像猪一样被宰了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What about Boggs and Rains? - Slaughtered like pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.30,0:59:51.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 不是我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It wasn't me. It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.27,0:59:56.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他完全疯了 早该用铁炼锁住\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Stark raving mad. It wasn't anyone's fault, but he should have been chained up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.10,0:59:59.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对 长官 他发疯了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You called it, sir. Mad as a fuckin' hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:02.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把他隔离 别引起恐慌\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Keep him separated. Don't want him causing a panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.07,1:00:04.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 克里蒙斯 - 是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Clemens! - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.53,1:00:08.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让这白痴安静下来 - 我们得先弄清楚弟兄的下落\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Sedate this poor idiot. - Not until we know about the brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.12,1:00:11.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 告诉我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now, pull yourself together. Talk to me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:14.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伯格和雷恩在哪里？ - 不是我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Where are Boggs and Rains? - It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.87,1:00:17.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用 问不出来的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're not gonna get anything out of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.75,1:00:19.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得派出搜索队\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We'll have to send out a search team.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.92,1:00:23.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这畜牲可能杀了他们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's a good chance this simple bastard has murdered them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.43,1:00:28.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.93,1:00:32.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他没骗过我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He's never lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.85,1:00:36.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个疯疯癫癫的傻子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He's crazy, he's a fool, but he's not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.94,1:00:40.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他不会说谎\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.48,1:00:43.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟他谈谈这条龙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'd like to talk to him about this... dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.73,1:00:46.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是一条龙 - 你别想跟任何人说话 中尉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- It's a dragon! - You're not talking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.82,1:00:51.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你的意见没兴趣 你根本搞不清状况\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm not interested in your opinion, because you are not in full possession of the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.99,1:00:56.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾犯下多宗杀人案 是个残忍的凶手\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He is a convicted murderer, known for particularly brutal crimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.41,1:01:01.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对不对 迪伦先生？ - 对…那是真的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Isn't that right, Mr. Dillon? - Yeah. That part's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.30,1:01:06.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就和你谈 这很重要\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then I'll talk to you. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.55,1:01:11.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我完成职务后很乐意和你谈\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When I have finished with my official duties, I'll be pleased to have a little chat. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.10,1:01:18.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我弄清楚 中尉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let me see if I have this correct, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.60,1:01:24.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这生物有8尺高 血液是强酸 坐你的太空船到达此地\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's an eight-foot creature with acid for blood, and it arrived on your spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.78,1:01:29.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它见人就杀 性情不太友善\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It kills on sight and is generally unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.53,1:01:32.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然期望我信你的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And you expect me to accept all this on your word.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.20,1:01:34.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不期望任何事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No. I don't expect anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.62,1:01:39.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 故事很精彩 亚伦先生 - 是的 很精彩\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Quite a story, Mr. Aaron. - Right, sir. It's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.37,1:01:42.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没听过这种故事 - 我想也没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Never heard anything quite like it, sir. - Expect not.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.50,1:01:46.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 你建议我们怎么做？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Tell me, Lieutenant, what would you suggest we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.05,1:01:51.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们有什么武器？ - 这是监狱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What kind of weapons have you got? - This is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.30,1:01:55.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不能让囚犯碰武器 - 以免他们杀了你？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- We don't allow prisoners access to firearms. - It keeps them from killing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.06,1:01:59.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 它根本逃不出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah. There's no way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.19,1:02:03.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,下一班补给船到达时 公司会派人消灭它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}With the arrival of the next supply ship, the company will eliminate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.11,1:02:08.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个最高设防的监狱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is a maximum-security prison...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.24,1:02:12.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们却没有任何武器？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and you have no weapons of any kind?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:20.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,屠宰场有几把屠刀 饭堂也有 还有几把斧头\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We have some carving knives in the abattoir, a few more in the mess hall, some fire axes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.87,1:02:23.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有太多厉害武器 - 只有这些？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Nothing terribly formidable. - That's all?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.88,1:02:26.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们推行荣誉制度\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We're on the honor system.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.01,1:02:33.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们完蛋了 - 不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Then we're fucked. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.84,1:02:38.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你完蛋了 我把你关在医疗室\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're fucked. Confined to the infirmary. Quarantined.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.81,1:02:41.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦先生会护送你去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Mr. Aaron will escort you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.95,1:02:46.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那儿最安全 对吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You'll be safe from any nasty beasts while you're there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.92,1:02:50.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这才乖\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.68,1:02:59.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,全体到饭堂报到 狱长安德鲁要开会\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let's all report to the mess hall. The superintendent wants a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.51,1:03:01.84,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻到饭堂报到\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Mess hall, right away, people.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.93,1:03:06.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能离开？有办法逃生？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Isn't there any way off of this place? Some way to escape?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.52,1:03:09.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,补给船每六个月来一次\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No. A supply ship comes every six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.02,1:03:11.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.98,1:03:14.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.95,1:03:18.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就有人来接你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They are sending somebody to pick you up quite soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.99,1:03:22.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很快是多快？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Really? What's soon?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.12,1:03:26.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 以前没有人急着来这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't know. Nobody's ever been in a hurry to get here before.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.17,1:03:33.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说 安德鲁和你谈些什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do you want to tell me what you and Andrews talked about?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.34,1:03:34.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.84,1:03:37.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你会说我疯了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You'd just say I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.93,1:03:41.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说有点不厚道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's a bit uncharitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.94,1:03:51.26,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.36,1:03:53.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不太好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Not so hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.65,1:03:58.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,喉咙痛 胃部不舒服\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sore throat, sick to my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.16,1:04:04.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 而且气坏了 - 在这种情况下我能了解\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Pissed off. - Understandable, given the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.20,1:04:07.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我 该给你打一剂特别的药\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Perhaps I should give you one of my special cocktails.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.87,1:04:10.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都互相指责？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't know why everybody blames everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.75,1:04:15.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,人非圣贤 我们只是凡人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nobody's perfect. We're only human.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.38,1:04:17.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个人是完美的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's no such thing as a perfect human.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.68,1:04:20.84,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是疯狂世界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In an insane world,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.93,1:04:27.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,正常人也要变成疯子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}a sane man must appear insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.06,1:04:30.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,讲得真好 葛立\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's very profound, Golic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.73,1:04:32.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.36,1:04:39.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你结婚了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You married?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.49,1:04:42.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我？ - 你应该结婚生子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Me? - You should get married, have kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.99,1:04:45.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么漂亮\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.54,1:04:48.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾认识 很多漂亮女孩\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I used to know lots of them. Back home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.46,1:04:51.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她们很喜欢我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They used to like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.92,1:04:57.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,过一阵子就变心\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}For a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.64,1:05:04.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你也会死的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're gonna die, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.81,1:05:12.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.02,1:05:16.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？ - 结婚\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What? - Married.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.82,1:05:20.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 干嘛？ - 只是好奇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Why? - Just curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.32,1:05:23.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.37,1:05:30.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你也坦白点 如何？ - 讲清楚一点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How about leveling with me? - Could you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.21,1:05:34.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你没说你为何被派来这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When I asked how you got assigned here, you avoided the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.46,1:05:41.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我提到你脑后的监狱识别条码 你又顾左右而言他\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then when I asked about the prison ID tattooed on your head, you ducked me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.68,1:05:48.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长 令人伤心 而且通俗煽情\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's a long, sad story. And more than a little melodramatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.52,1:05:50.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,说来听听\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Try me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.35,1:05:55.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么想听\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.07,1:06:02.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我毕业以后\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}After my student years,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.49,1:06:09.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我已经对吗啡上瘾\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}despite the fact that I had become secretly addicted to morphine,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.29,1:06:13.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍被认为 是最有前途的医生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I was considered to be most promising. A man with a future.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.79,1:06:21.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我当专科实习医生 在急诊室当值36小时\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}During my first residency I did a 36-hour stretch on an ER.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.43,1:06:26.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我跑出去 喝得酩酊大醉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So I went out and I got more than a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.39,1:06:28.26,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我又被召回\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then I got called back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.35,1:06:33.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一座炼油厂的蒸汽炉爆炸 30名伤者\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Boiler had blown in a fuel plant and there were 30 casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.81,1:06:35.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,11人死亡\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And 11 of them died.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.90,1:06:41.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为意外 而是因为我开错止痛药剂量\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Not as a result of the accident, but because I prescribed the wrong dosage of painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.03,1:06:48.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我服刑七年 执照被降为3C\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I got seven years in prison and my license reduced to a three-C.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.75,1:06:54.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 至少我戒掉吗啡瘾 - 很遗憾\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- At least I got off the morphine. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.29,1:06:58.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我的惩罚还算轻\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I think I was let off lightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.38,1:07:03.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里服刑？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Did you serve your time here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.59,1:07:06.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我和这群乌合之众混熟了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I got to know this motley crew quite well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.55,1:07:10.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们留下来 我也留下了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So when they stayed, I stayed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.97,1:07:14.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人愿意聘用我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nobody else would employ me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.61,1:07:21.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你还愿意让我打针吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So, do you still trust me with a needle?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.45,1:08:53.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.37,1:09:00.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,主呀 给我们力量来坚守\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Give us strength, O Lord, to endure
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.21,1:09:04.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是上帝手中 卑微的罪人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We recognize that we are poor sinners in the hands of an angry god
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.84,1:09:07.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,请以手包围我们 守护我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let the circle be unbroken until the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.80,1:09:09.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿们 - 阿们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.84,1:09:12.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里出了什么事？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the fuck is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.43,1:09:17.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,出了这么一大堆事情\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the fuck is this bullshit that's coming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.68,1:09:21.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有人死了 有人要强暴 弟兄出了麻烦\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We got a murder, we got a rape, we got brothers in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.94,1:09:25.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再闹事了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't want no more bullshit around here!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.19,1:09:29.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,出了问题 我们要团结\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now, we got problems, we stand together.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.32,1:09:31.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 谢谢 迪伦先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yes. Thank you, Mr. Dillon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.99,1:09:36.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 这是谣言管制会议\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All right. Once again this is Rumor Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.16,1:09:38.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,以下是案情\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Here are the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.79,1:09:44.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,早上八点 囚犯墨菲因为粗心\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}At 0800 hours, prisoner Murphy, through carelessness on his part,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.67,1:09:47.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,在第17通风孔死去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}was found dead in vent shaft 17.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.38,1:09:51.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎被吸入通风扇门\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}He seems to have been sucked into a ventilator fan.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.39,1:10:00.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上九点 囚犯葛立出现 精神错乱\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}At about 2100 hours, prisoner Golic reappeared in a deranged state.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.44,1:10:02.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯伯格和雷恩失踪\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Prisoners Boggs and Rains are missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.85,1:10:07.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是遇害\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There seems to be a good chance that they have met with foul play
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.57,1:10:10.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,遭囚犯葛立杀害\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}at the hands of prisoner Golic.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.41,1:10:15.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须组组一支搜索队\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We need to organize and send out a search party.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.74,1:10:20.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有人自愿我们会很感激\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Volunteers will be appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.92,1:10:26.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这座监狱一直相安无事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I think it's fair to say that our smoothly running facility
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.96,1:10:30.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现一些问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}has suddenly developed a few problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.09,1:10:35.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家 能在这几天提起精神\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I can only hope we are able to all pull together over the next few days,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.26,1:10:39.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,直到救援小组 接走蕾普莉中尉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}until the rescue team arrives for Lt Ripley.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.10,1:10:42.55,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它来了 它杀死克里蒙斯 - 马上停止这种谣言\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- It's here! It got Clemens! - Stop this raving at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.64,1:10:45.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说它来了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm telling you! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.19,1:10:48.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦 把那笨女人带回医疗室\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Aaron, get that foolish woman back to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.82,1:10:53.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么？ - 快跑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What is that? - Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.24,1:11:02.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.42,1:11:10.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,主呀 我们感谢你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We give you thanks, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.55,1:11:16.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,您的愤怒已显现 我们知道审判快到\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The wrath has come, the time is near for us to be judged.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.64,1:11:20.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日将要降临\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The Apocalypse is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.72,1:11:24.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们有所准备\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let us be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.10,1:11:27.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,得到您的饶恕\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let your mercy be just.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.40,1:11:29.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好可怕 - 阿们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- It was massive. - Amen!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.36,1:11:31.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在那里 我看到了 - 我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I was there. I saw it. - Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.61,1:11:37.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在该怎么办？ 谁来指挥？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the fuck do we do now? Who's in fucking charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.12,1:11:42.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得组组起来 对吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Organize! We gotta organize, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.75,1:11:45.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我有指挥权\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right! I'm next in line.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.42,1:11:49.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让85指挥？完了 - 别那么叫我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- 85's gonna be in charge. Give us a break! - Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.21,1:11:53.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能取代安德鲁 他是好人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's no way I can replace Andrews. He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.26,1:11:57.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 虽然你们不喜欢他 - 亚伦 我们不想听屁话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I know you didn't appreciate him... - Aaron, we don't wanna hear that shit now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.68,1:12:02.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,妹子 你呢？你是个军官 展露一点领导才能吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sister, what about you? You an officer. How about showing us a little leadership?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.14,1:12:04.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别管她 你来指挥\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Forget fuckin' Shirley Temple! You take charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.85,1:12:06.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对 - 反正这里都是你在管\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Right. - You run things here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.02,1:12:11.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我没当官的材料\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No fuckin' way. I'm not the officer type.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.53,1:12:15.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我只会管我自己\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I just take care of my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.57,1:12:18.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这臭怪物想要什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Well, what does this fuckin' beast want?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.70,1:12:22.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这老妈到底指不指挥？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Is this mother gonna try for us all?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.21,1:12:27.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.33,1:12:29.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这下可好 你想怎么阻止它？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ain't that sweet! How are we gonna stop it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.17,1:12:38.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们没有武器 对吧？ - 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You have no weapons. Is that correct? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.97,1:12:41.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的和这只不一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I haven't seen one exactly like this before.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.85,1:12:44.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它的动作有点不同\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It moves differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.39,1:12:50.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,其他那些什么都不怕 只怕火\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But the others were afraid of fire. Not much else.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.27,1:12:58.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 能不能封锁这地方？ - 没办法 共有六百个通气管\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Can we seal off this area? - No chance. There's 600 air ducts...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.86,1:13:03.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,录影设备呢？ 这里到处都有闭路电视系统\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Video? There's closed-circuit monitors everywhere. We could use that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.53,1:13:08.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,闭路电视系统多年没用 这里什么都不能用\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The video system hasn't worked in years. Nothing much works here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.16,1:13:10.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很多科技用品 都没办法修好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've got technology, no way to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.50,1:13:12.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 85想说的是… - 别那么叫我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- 85 is trying to tell you... - Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.00,1:13:17.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有娱乐中心 气候控制 没有视讯系统\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We ain't got no entertainment center. No climate control, no video system.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.34,1:13:22.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有监视 没有电雪柜 没有雪糕\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No surveillance. No freezers. No fuckin' ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.10,1:13:24.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有避孕套 没有女人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No rubbers, no women.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.31,1:13:27.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有枪 什么都没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No guns. All we got here is shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.98,1:13:32.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她谈有个屁用？ 她把那臭东西带来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the hell are we even talking to her for? She brought the fucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.77,1:13:37.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,何不砍下她的头 塞进墙壁？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why don't we just get her head and shove it through the fuckin' wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.49,1:13:39.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这样最好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.90,1:13:40.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Morse.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.78,1:13:57.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.37,1:14:01.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.84,1:14:17.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.35,1:14:22.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那条通道从饭堂通往医疗室 是个通风孔\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That leads from the mess hall to the infirmary. It's a ventilation shaft.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.60,1:14:25.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从那里进去 把它逼出来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then we go in there. Flush it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.06,1:14:31.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的隧道有好几里长\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hey, look, there's miles and miles of tunnel through there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.19,1:14:33.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它走不了太远\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It won't go far.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.99,1:14:36.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它会在这里筑巢\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It'll nest in this area.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.41,1:14:40.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就在…这附近\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right around... here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.20,1:14:43.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.29,1:14:49.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它就像只狮子 紧跟着斑马群\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's like a lion. It sticks close to the zebras.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.25,1:14:52.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,斑马？别开玩笑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Zebras? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.13,1:14:56.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这么暗跑来跑去？ 走出主通风孔就没有电灯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But running around here in the dark? Outside of this main shaft there's no overheads.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.97,1:15:01.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是有手电筒吗？ - 有几千个 没有电池\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Don't we have flashlights? - Thousands of them, but no batteries.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.39,1:15:06.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,火把呢？我们能生火吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Torches? Do we have the capacity to make fire?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.27,1:15:10.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,人类从石器时代起 就有这能力\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Most humans have enjoyed that privilege since the Stone Age.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.69,1:15:12.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着讽刺我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No need to be sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.66,1:15:19.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没用过 这里打算放核废料\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Never been used. They were gonna dump nuclear crap in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.37,1:15:21.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一直没空 里头空无一物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Never did. It's clean as a whistle inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.87,1:15:24.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是出入的唯一通道？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is the only way in or out?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.29,1:15:28.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 墙壁有6尺多厚 实心钢造的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's right. Walls are six feet thick. Solid steel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.13,1:15:30.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道怎么保护这些婴儿\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They knew how to build these babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.13,1:15:35.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,任何东西被关进去 绝对出不来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're saying we get something in there, there's no way it can get out?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.30,1:15:39.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 无路可逃\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's right. No fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.35,1:15:48.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们放在这里 忘了叫什么\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's kept here. Forget what it's called.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.90,1:15:51.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 圭乃特利西特林 - 我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Quinitricetyline. - I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.53,1:15:58.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我把工作分配好 让迪伦髹油\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I've gotta get these section arrangements organized with Dillon for the paint brush, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.66,1:16:00.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在… - 大卫\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- So, um... - David...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.37,1:16:04.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你把这些油桶整理好 - 知道了 85\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You can get these drums organized. - Right, 85.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.04,1:16:07.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还有…别那么叫我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And, uh... don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.96,1:16:14.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,85到底是什么意思？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's this "85" thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.84,1:16:20.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们偷看过他的档案 那是他的智商\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}A couple of us sneaked a look at his personnel file. It's his IQ.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.48,1:16:31.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过这种油桶 掉在海滩木屋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I saw a drum of this stuff fall into a beachhead bunker once.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.98,1:16:35.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸令码头三个半月 没有鱼群\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The blast put a tug in dry dock for 17 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.49,1:16:37.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的玩意\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Great stuff!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.03,1:16:44.19,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我搞清楚\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All right, let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.25,1:16:48.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你想用火把它烧出通风管\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You wanna burn it down and out of the pipes,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.23,1:16:51.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,逼进这里 把门锁上 然后把它困住？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}force it in here, slam the door, and trap its ass?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.54,1:16:53.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.67,1:16:57.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我们 这些天生罪犯帮忙？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And you want help from us Y-chromo boys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.55,1:16:59.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你有别的事要做吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You got something better to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.55,1:17:02.47,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为何要替你 冒险拼命？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why should we put our ass on the line for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.55,1:17:04.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们早就有危险\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Your ass is already on the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.68,1:17:07.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是你打算怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The only question is what are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.59,1:17:26.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 两千个电池 只有一个用得着\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Look at this. There's only one of these batteries in 2,000 that works.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.26,1:17:28.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还未算最糟\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hey, it could have been a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.43,1:17:32.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可能照不亮\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We might have got the paintbrush detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.82,1:17:38.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意真臭\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Man, this stuff stinks!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.41,1:17:54.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真是臭死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This shit smells awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.50,1:17:59.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的要臭死人了 - 应该要戴氧气筒\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I can't believe the fucking fumes. - You need a fuckin' pipe for breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.42,1:18:02.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不要深呼吸\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Don't breathe too hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.73,1:18:17.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你想念医生 对吧？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You miss Doc, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.86,1:18:22.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.44,1:18:25.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个很亲密\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I thought you two got real close.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.91,1:18:29.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你很爱偷窥\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I guess you've been looking through some keyholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.99,1:18:32.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是那么想的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.46,1:18:43.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗？ - 还好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Are you OK? - Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.05,1:18:47.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？ 可是你看起来不太好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Whatever you say, but you don't look OK to me, sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.39,1:18:51.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.98,1:18:57.47,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这地方\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I hate this place. I hate this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.78,1:19:05.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们 绝对还有别的东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}There's definitely something in here with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.70,1:19:13.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我没打信号别点火 这是信号\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Don't light the fire until I give the signal. This is the signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.66,1:19:16.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗？记得住吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Got it? Can you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.92,1:19:22.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.13,1:20:05.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.90,1:20:26.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不等信号？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Wait for the fucking signal!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.91,1:20:36.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.87,1:20:45.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 我们得找出洒水器 快救他们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on! We gotta find the sprinklers. We gotta help these guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.01,1:20:56.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 跑呀\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on. Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.39,1:21:00.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,到废料处理场 别开门\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get to the waste dump. Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.83,1:22:07.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're all right. You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.50,1:22:11.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,火熄了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The fire's out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.10,1:22:24.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,朱德\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Jude. Jude!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.10,1:22:26.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,去把洒水器打开\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get to the sprinklers and turn 'em on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.81,1:22:28.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快带他出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We gotta get him outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.91,1:22:38.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们带你出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We're getting you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.68,1:22:48.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它在你后面\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Jude! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.34,1:22:51.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.97,1:23:05.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.94,1:23:07.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,来捉我呀\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come and get me, fucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.41,1:24:44.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们受难\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Even for those who have fallen,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.41,1:24:47.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍应欣慰\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}this is a time of rejoicing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.71,1:24:51.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,向他们的勇气致敬\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We salute their courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.09,1:24:57.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会永垂不朽\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They will live forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.30,1:25:04.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡并不代表真正死去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Those that are dead are not dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.85,1:25:06.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们升上天去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They have moved up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.81,1:25:11.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,到了更高的境界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They have moved to a higher place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.65,1:25:13.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,疯子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Crazy bastards.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.90,1:25:16.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,克里蒙斯常叫做迪伦圣兵\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Clemens used to call them Dillon's God Squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.94,1:25:19.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,令他们幸免于难\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It keeps 'em out of mischief.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.86,1:25:22.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不信宗教？ - 我？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You're not the religious type? - Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.57,1:25:25.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,才不 我要工作\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shit, no. I got a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.08,1:25:31.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我想救援队四五天就会到了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Look. I figure the rescue team gets here in four, five days.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.08,1:25:34.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,顶多是六天\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Six, tops.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.17,1:25:38.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一来 拿出机关枪\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They open the door, go in there with smart guns,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.17,1:25:40.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,轰死它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}and kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.80,1:25:43.84,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有消息吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What have you heard from them?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.93,1:25:47.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只说收到讯息\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nothing much. We got a "Message received".
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.77,1:25:53.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,后来又说 你是最高优先考虑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Later we got something that said you were top priority.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.19,1:25:56.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不说 因为我们在边疆\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They don't cut us in on much. We're the arse end of the totem pole here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.73,1:26:00.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们不想杀怪物呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What if they don't want to kill it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.90,1:26:06.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 带回去吗？ - 是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Take it back? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.24,1:26:09.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们疯了 一定要杀了它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They're not lunatics. They gotta kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.25,1:26:12.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.13,1:26:21.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯 把我放开\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Morse, please cut me loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.51,1:26:26.26,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不可以 - 很痛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- No fucking way. - Come on. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.34,1:26:28.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry.
