Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.90,1:26:47.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我只告诉他 那条龙杀了伯格和雷恩\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All I did was tell him about the dragon, what it did to Boggs and Rains.
