Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.16,1:26:58.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 它一进来 我就死了 我跑不了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on, please! If this gets in here, I'm dead. I can't run.
