Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.31,1:28:02.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不给你香烟了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No more cigarettes for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.03,1:28:14.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,第一步完成了 要说什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We got the first part. Now what do we say?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.45,1:28:16.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们是我们捉的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Tell them we trapped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.08,1:28:22.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那叫什么？ - 异形怪物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What do we call it? - A xenomorph.
