Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.58,1:29:46.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.71,1:29:49.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 抱歉 抱歉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.16,1:30:17.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我要怎么做\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Tell me what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.15,1:30:48.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要来带走怪物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So they're coming to take this thing away.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.77,1:30:52.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会这么做 根本就不杀死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah, they're gonna try. They don't wanna kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.32,1:30:54.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得想办法\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We gotta figure out a way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.70,1:30:58.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要杀它？ 反正公司会来解决\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why do we have to kill it? You just said the company's coming for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.70,1:31:02.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 他们是来带走怪物 用作研究武器\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That's right. They wanna take it back, as some sort of weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.04,1:31:08.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有何不可？ - 他们不知道它的危险性\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's wrong with that? - They don't understand it'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.38,1:31:10.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 有何不可？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Like I said, what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.65,1:31:14.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 但很多无辜的人会死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nothing's wrong with that, except a lot of innocent people will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.64,1:31:24.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以为你有宗教信仰 - 你不明白\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I thought you were a religious man. - You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.35,1:31:31.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界 对我们已经不存在\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That world out there doesn't exist for us any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.94,1:31:34.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有自己的世界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We got our own little world down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.36,1:31:37.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不大 却是我们的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It ain't much, but it's ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.16,1:31:41.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别人都可以死吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So fuck everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.08,1:31:45.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不 所有人都可以\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No. Fuck them.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.33,1:31:50.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 迪伦 - 是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Hey, Dillon? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.88,1:31:54.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,迪伦\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Dillon.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.05,1:31:57.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有个小问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We got a teeny-weeny problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.36,1:32:15.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这下好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuckin' great!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.45,1:32:21.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那疯小子放走怪物 自作自受\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The miserable, crazy son of a bitch let it loose. Got what he fuckin' deserved.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.54,1:32:25.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.75,1:32:30.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁是对的 应该把那小子锁住的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Andrews was right. Should have kept the shithead chained up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.46,1:32:37.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吗？ - 去她的 那怪物还在外面\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You OK? - Piss on her. The fuckin' thing's loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.55,1:32:40.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 该怎么办？ - 我说过了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What are we gonna do? - I just said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.43,1:32:44.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你这小王八蛋让葛立逃跑\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're the dumb prick that let Golic out. You miserable little shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.60,1:32:49.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了 住嘴 - 叫那个小丑识相点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Cut that shit out. - Tell your fuckin' bozo to shape up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.06,1:32:55.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你觉得呢？ - 到逃生艇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What do you think? - I think I have to get to the EEV.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.73,1:32:59.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么？ - 我们得用神经扫描器\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Why? What's up? - I just have to use the neuroscanner.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.03,1:33:04.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看来很憔悴 - 管她好不好 现在怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You don't look so good. - Who gives a shit! What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.58,1:33:09.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你想挨揍吗 笨蛋？ 闭上你的臭嘴 别让大家惊慌\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do you want a smack in the mouth, you stupid wanker? Stop causing panic!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.50,1:33:15.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,惊慌？ 你笨得连惊慌也不会写\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Panic? You're so stupid, you couldn't spell it. Don't talk to me about panic!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.50,1:33:17.46,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个闭嘴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shut up, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.22,1:33:21.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.73,1:33:41.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们都没有办法了 - 不出奇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Well, I'm out of ideas. - Surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.49,1:33:45.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 外面怎么样？ - 太厉害了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What about outside? - Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.78,1:33:50.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,两天后日出 现在零下40度\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Sun doesn't come up for two days, it's 40 below zero. That makes a lot of sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.54,1:33:54.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 让那怪物把我们当午餐\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So you just want us to stay here and let this thing have us for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.79,1:34:01.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,叫所有仍生还的人集合 到大厅聚集\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Get everybody that's still left together. Get 'em into the assembly hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.14,1:34:05.21,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.93,1:34:09.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,她上哪里去了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.67,1:34:39.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,需要帮忙吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Need any help?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.67,1:34:46.05,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意吓你 你不应该一个人乱走\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I didn't mean to scare you. You shouldn't be wandering around alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.14,1:34:50.55,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙 替我按键盘\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do me a favor and run this keyboard, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.06,1:34:53.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.28,1:35:07.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我该怎么做？ - 按B或C C是什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What do I do? - Hit B or C. What's C?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.20,1:35:10.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 显示生命机能 - 就是那个\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- "Display bio-functions"? - That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.75,1:35:16.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 现在呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK, we're hot. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.96,1:35:19.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让它转一圈\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let it run its cycle.
