Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.82,1:36:37.82,硬字幕4,,0600,0000,0500,,{\fs48\frz16\4c&H000000&}DNA资料扫描中
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.78,1:36:39.53,硬字幕4,,0600,0000,0420,,{\fs48\frz16\4c&H000000&}组织类型不明
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.42,1:36:43.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太可怕了 - 我得看看它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Horrible. - I have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.46,1:36:49.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 定格 - 你最好别看\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Freeze it! - You don't want to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.43,1:37:17.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难过\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.36,1:37:25.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物还在 它逃出来了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All right, the fuckin' thing is loose. It's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.78,1:37:28.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,救援队带着武器 快到达了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}A rescue team is on its way with guns and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.03,1:37:33.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在危机四伏\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Right now, there isn't any place that's real safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.24,1:37:35.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在这里集合\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We stay here in the assembly hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.79,1:37:38.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这里他妈的没有空调\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This place never had any fuckin' air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.75,1:37:41.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,如果怪物来了 一定走大门\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If it comes in, it'll be through these doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.17,1:37:44.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要有人守门 怪物来了才知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We'll post a guard who'll let us know if it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.13,1:37:49.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在先躲好 准备好迎接它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}In the meantime, you lay low, be ready and stay right,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.92,1:37:52.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,万一你的大限来临\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}in case your time comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.01,1:37:58.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,迪伦 少鬼话连篇 我们都会被困死在这里的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Don't you start bullshitting, Dillon. We're gonna be trapped in here like rats.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.31,1:38:02.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,有武器小刀的 拿出来用吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You got a weapon. You got a blade. You take it out and you fuckin' use it!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.40,1:38:06.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对 用小刀就能杀死怪物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Oh, right. So you think we're gonna stab this motherfucker to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.94,1:38:09.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死个鬼\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't think shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.69,1:38:13.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只能在被杀死前令它受伤\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Maybe you'll hurt it before it takes you out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.24,1:38:16.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个主意 谁有更好的主意？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Isn't that something? Any of you got any better ideas?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.96,1:38:26.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你们 等救援队到达前我们已经死光\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I'll tell you. Until the rescue team gets here, we're fucked!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.25,1:38:31.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,大家先作准备吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So you better get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.47,1:38:40.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不留在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Well, I ain't stayin' here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.23,1:38:45.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Then suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.49,1:38:54.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,点火\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.24,1:39:02.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是熔炉 - 对 快过去看\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- The furnace. - Yeah. Let's make it to the furnace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.17,1:39:07.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,老天哪\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.38,1:39:13.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这下好了 - 真他妈的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Well, all right. - Fuckin' A.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.22,1:39:17.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,真他妈的 说得对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Too fuckin' right, it's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.45,1:39:39.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,设定好了 你想说什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's up. What do you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.42,1:39:43.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们说这里充满毒气\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Tell them the whole place has gone toxic.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.46,1:39:46.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑 救援小组会折返\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Are you kidding? The rescue team will turn back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.97,1:39:50.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道 - 你在胡说什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Yeah, I know. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.60,1:39:54.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得靠他们杀死怪物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Our only hope is that they kill this fucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.27,1:39:59.47,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也许能想办法 把你冷藏起来动手术\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Maybe they can do something for you. I don't know, freeze you, do an operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.56,1:40:03.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要是异形逃走 就会杀光所有人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If this organism gets off the planet, it'll kill everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.94,1:40:06.18,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,公司根本不在乎\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The company doesn't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.28,1:40:09.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只想拿它 来研究生化武器\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They just want it for their bio-weapons division, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.57,1:40:12.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让他们来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So we can't let them come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.95,1:40:14.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,管你的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.49,1:40:18.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我很遗憾你体内有那东西 可是他们得救我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm sorry you've got this thing inside you, but I'm getting rescued.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.08,1:40:22.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管那些囚犯 我有老婆、孩子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't care about these prisoners, but I've got a wife and a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.71,1:40:25.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 下次轮到我回家 - 我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I go home on the next rotation. - I know. This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.92,1:40:29.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要传送这讯息 我要密码\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But I'm gonna send this message and I need that fucking code.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.72,1:40:32.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这是机密\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm sorry, Ripley. It's classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.80,1:40:35.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋一定要这么做\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You stupid little shit, this has got to be done!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.68,1:40:38.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别无选择\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK? There are no alternatives!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.94,1:40:41.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会给你密码 不可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're not getting it! No fucking way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.74,1:40:49.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我跟你无冤无仇\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Look, it's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.07,1:40:53.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你会没有事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Understand? I think you're OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.11,1:41:01.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.67,1:41:12.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么主意吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Have you got any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.72,1:41:15.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它不会杀我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.97,1:41:20.84,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我孕育新女王\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm carrying the new queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.94,1:41:23.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它不会杀死自己的未来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It won't kill its future.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.69,1:41:27.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物有这么聪明？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You really wanna bet this thing's that smart?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.86,1:41:30.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我去找它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Maybe I'll go find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.07,1:41:33.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,看它到底有多聪明\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}See how smart it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.24,1:41:36.66,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要去找它？ - 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You're gonna go and look for it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.58,1:41:40.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道它在哪里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have a pretty good idea of where it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.37,1:41:45.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它就在下面 地下室\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's just down there, in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.33,1:41:48.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这整个地方都是地下室\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This whole place is a basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.46,1:41:51.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是打个比喻\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's a metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.76,1:41:53.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你来不来？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.93,1:41:58.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuck me!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.06,1:42:06.02,硬字幕4,,0000,1000,0220,,收到逃生艇扫描资料
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.14,1:42:06.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0780,0170,,紧急医疗小组 将在2小时内到达
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.70,1:42:22.50,硬字幕4,,0000,1000,0220,,收到逃生艇扫描资料
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.70,1:42:22.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0780,0170,,紧急医疗小组 将在2小时内到达
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.41,1:42:25.17,硬字幕4,,0000,1100,0320,,最高优先考虑
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.04,1:42:25.17,硬字幕4,,0000,1055,0270,,隔离蕾普莉中尉
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.21,1:42:31.67,硬字幕4,,0000,1100,0130,,等   待   确   认
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.63,1:42:31.67,硬字幕4,,0000,1100,0080,,等   待   确   认
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.30,1:42:31.67,硬字幕4,,0000,1100,0030,,等   待   确   认
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.44,1:43:24.98,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,要找你时你在哪里呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Where are you when I need you?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.77,1:44:00.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.52,1:44:03.76,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的家人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.55,1:45:15.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你进入我的生命这么久 我已经不记得其他事情\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You've been in my life so long, I can't remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.43,1:45:20.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在帮我个忙吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.27,1:45:24.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,很简单\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.44,1:45:27.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只要…\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.23,1:45:29.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只要发挥你的本能\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Just do what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.41,1:46:18.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它不肯杀我 - 你应该躲起来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- It won't kill me. - You're supposed to be laying low.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.45,1:46:21.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我体内也有一只\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I have one inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.04,1:46:24.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,大只的怪物不肯杀我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The big one won't kill its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.88,1:46:29.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在说什么？ - 我刚刚看到了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What are you talking about? - I just saw it, an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.59,1:46:31.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我就站在它旁边\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I stood right next to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.01,1:46:36.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它可以杀我 可是它不杀我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I could have been lunch, but it wouldn't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.26,1:46:38.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它跑掉了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It ran away.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.81,1:46:43.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它知道我在孕育它的后代 - 胡说\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- It knows I'm carrying its future. - Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.89,1:46:49.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你怎么知道你体内也有？ - 我透过断层扫描看到它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How do you know the thing's inside you? - I saw it, on the CAT scan.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.90,1:46:54.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它是个女王 会产卵\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's a queen. An egg-layer.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.49,1:46:56.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它会生出上千个这种怪物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It can make thousands more.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.66,1:46:59.82,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来还是胡说八道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It still sounds like bullshit to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.50,1:47:05.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那东西是怎么进入你体内？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}If that thing's inside you, how did it get there?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.42,1:47:10.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我在长眠的时候吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When I was in hypersleep, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.17,1:47:12.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它攻击我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I was violated.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.88,1:47:18.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我成为女王之母\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And now I get to be the mother of the leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.97,1:47:23.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我的时间不多\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.64,1:47:27.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,无法做我该做的事\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I can't do what I should.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.57,1:47:31.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮忙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I need you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.57,1:47:38.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你得杀死我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I need you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.45,1:47:42.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在胡说什么？ - 反正我死定了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What the fuck are you talking about? - I'm dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.33,1:47:44.49,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我活不了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I can't survive it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.75,1:47:48.83,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我体内的异形 会繁殖上千只后代\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}But the one inside of me can generate thousands more.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.29,1:47:53.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可以杀光整个宇宙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It can wipe out the whole universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.46,1:47:55.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它一定得死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It has to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.97,1:47:58.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,必须有人杀死我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So somebody's gotta kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.43,1:48:04.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你办得到吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Are you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.35,1:48:07.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这点你不必担心\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.58,1:48:26.65,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不必致词\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No speeches.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.83,1:48:32.24,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,也不必祷告\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No prayers.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.95,1:49:07.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么回事？ - 我不喜欢服输\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What's going on? - I don't like losing a fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.37,1:49:09.78,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对任何人或物都一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Not to nobody, not to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.87,1:49:14.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那东西杀死半数的弟兄 另一半也被吓得半死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That thing has already killed half my men and got the other half scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.84,1:49:20.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只要它还活着 你就别想拯救宇宙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}As long as it's alive, sister, you're not gonna save any universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.22,1:49:23.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是胆小鬼 - 我要捉住它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You fuckin' coward! - I want that thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.06,1:49:27.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮我逮住它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I wanna get this thing and I need you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.60,1:49:32.23,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它不肯杀你 也许对我们有利\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And if it won't kill you, then maybe that helps us fight it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.31,1:49:34.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就少说废话\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Otherwise, fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.07,1:49:39.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你不帮忙就去死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Go kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.37,1:49:46.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,迪伦\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Dillon!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.83,1:49:51.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,干掉这怪物之后 你就得除掉我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We waste this thing, then you take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.79,1:49:53.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.79,1:49:56.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你会死得痛快 不受折磨\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Quick, easy and painless.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.09,1:50:04.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,由你自己决定\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is the choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.26,1:50:07.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想坐以待毙 还是奋战到死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You die sitting here on your ass, or you die out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.06,1:50:10.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我们该试试 让它好看\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}At least we take a shot. We owe it one!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.44,1:50:14.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它把我们都害惨了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's fucked us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.61,1:50:18.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,应该来个以牙还牙 要怎么做？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Maybe we can get even for the others. Now, how do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.82,1:50:23.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在胡说什么？ - 我是说去杀了那混帐东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What the fuck are you talking about? - Killing that big motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.57,1:50:29.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 救援队要来了 我们只要等就好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hold it, hold it. The rescue team's on its way. We could just sit this out.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.54,1:50:32.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要救援谁呢？ - 我们呀\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- The rescue team for who? - For us.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.17,1:50:39.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们只想要怪物 - 我才不管他们要什么\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- They just want the beast. You know that. - I don't give a damn what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.84,1:50:43.71,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们不会逐个接走吧 - 这我不敢说\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- They're not gonna pick us off one by one. - I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.80,1:50:47.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们是来带我们回家的 - 不是我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Come on! They'll take us home. - They're not gonna take "us" home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.51,1:50:50.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必跟它拼命\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Still doesn't mean we should fight it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.31,1:50:54.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是笨蛋 我有老婆孩子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I've got a wife and a kid...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.91,1:50:59.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人睬你 85 你只是个臭员工\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're a fuckin' company man!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.99,1:51:04.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我是员工 不是臭囚犯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah, OK. I'm a company man, I'm not a fuckin' criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.54,1:51:09.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直骂我笨 起码我够聪明 不像你们永远被关在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You tell me how dumb I am. I'm smart enough not to have a life sentence on this rock!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.42,1:51:11.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你的头 - 滚开 85！\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Shut your face! - Piss off, 85!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.05,1:51:17.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我够聪明 我会等武器来了再上战场\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And I'm smart enough to wait for some firepower to show up before we fight it!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.76,1:51:20.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你就乖乖坐在这儿\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK, just sit here on your asses. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.60,1:51:25.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也要乖乖坐在这里儿 - 没问题\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- How about if I sit here on my ass? - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.14,1:51:27.10,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Oh, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.19,1:51:31.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你向上帝祈求获得永生\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're the guy that's made a deal with God to live forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.77,1:51:36.02,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,其余的胆小鬼 也可以坐着不动\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And all the rest of you pussies can sit it out, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.11,1:51:39.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她会负责打仗\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Me and her'll do all the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.16,1:51:44.20,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 不过我要杀死它 我恨透那东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}OK. Look, I want the same thing as you. I want to see it dead. I hate the fucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.29,1:51:46.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它也杀死我的好朋友\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It killed my mates, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.62,1:51:50.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,为何不等到公司 把枪运来再动手？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Why the fuck can't we wait for the company and have some guns on our side?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.50,1:51:53.70,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为何一定要白白送死？ - 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Why should we go on a fucking suicide run? - Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.80,1:51:59.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,因为公司不会杀死它 他们可能杀了你们灭口\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Because they won't kill it. They might kill you for having seen it, but they won't kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.14,1:52:03.43,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,太荒谬了 胡说八道 他们不会杀我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}That is crazy! That is horseshit! They will not kill us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.89,1:52:11.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,当他们第一次听到有异形 就说可以牺牲船员\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When they first heard about this thing, it was "crew expendable".
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.11,1:52:16.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,上次派去的海军陆战队 也一样可以牺牲\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The next time, they sent in marines. They were expendable, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.07,1:52:20.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他们会在乎\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What makes you think they'll care about a bunch of lifers
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.36,1:52:23.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,关在外太空的囚犯吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}who found God at the ass-end of space?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.33,1:52:28.87,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他们会让你们 破坏他们的计划吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You really think they're gonna let you interfere with their plans for this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.87,1:52:32.58,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为我们是垃圾\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}They think we're crud.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.67,1:52:37.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不在乎你们的死活\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And they don't give a fuck about one friend of yours that's... that's died.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.43,1:52:41.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在乎\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Not one.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.76,1:52:48.93,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有计划吗？ - 这是个铸铅厂 不是吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Have you got some sort of plan? - This is a lead works, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.02,1:52:54.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把异形丢进模子 让它溺死在滚烫的铅里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}All we gotta do is lure the fuckin' beast into the mold. Drown it in hot lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.03,1:52:58.73,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我们该怎么做？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Oh, right. So how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.82,1:53:01.06,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 谁来当饵？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yeah. What are we gonna use for bait?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.50,1:53:09.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Aw, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.79,1:53:13.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们迟早都得死\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.25,1:53:16.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是怎样死法\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The only question is when.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.21,1:53:23.26,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方很适合 做上天堂的第一步\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is as good a place as any to take our first steps to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.35,1:53:26.68,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,问题只是要如何上去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The only question is how you check out.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.02,1:53:30.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要死得轰轰烈烈\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do you want it on your feet
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.98,1:53:33.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还是跪地求饶呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}or on your fucking knees, begging?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.96,1:53:37.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会求饶\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I ain't much for begging.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.82,1:53:40.14,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有人饶过我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Nobody ever gave me nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.24,1:53:43.77,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我说干掉那怪物 跟他拼命\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}So I say fuck that thing! Let's fight it!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.20,1:53:53.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧 我们跟它拼了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Fuck it. Let's go, boys! - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.63,1:53:59.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它冲过来怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the fuck are we gonna do if it runs at us?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.76,1:54:02.96,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,最好先想出好办法来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Better have some fucking good ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.49,1:54:09.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一号门开启\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Door 1 open.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.24,1:54:11.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们几时用过这地方？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}When was the last time you used this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.58,1:54:13.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,五、六年前用过\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We fired it up five, six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.00,1:54:18.37,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你确定活塞还能用？ - 没有一样东西能确定\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You sure the piston's gonna work? - There's nothing for sure in this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.13,1:54:25.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它被困进去你就拉下把手\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We trap it here first, then you pull the lever.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.63,1:54:30.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,关起活塞 把它推下模子 然后把铅倒进去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}The piston's gonna push it into the mold. One of the guys will pour the lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.60,1:54:34.13,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很简单 它死定了 - 要是有人搞砸呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- End of his ass, end of story. - What if somebody screws it up?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.23,1:54:37.01,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那就完蛋了 我们只有一次机会\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We're fucked. You got one chance, one shot at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.15,1:54:43.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间重新再来 记住 当你拉下把手\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We'll never have time to reset it. Now, remember, you pull the lever,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.40,1:54:47.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你也会和那怪物 困在里面一会儿\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}for a few seconds you're gonna be trapped in here with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.45,1:54:49.69,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不出差错 我也不会\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You guys don't drop the ball, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.78,1:54:52.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它最好真的不肯杀你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You better be right about that thing not wanting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.66,1:54:57.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它想逃出去只有一条路 通过凹槽 通过你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Because if it wants out, that's how it's gonna go: Through that alcove, through you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.50,1:55:01.36,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在那里？ - 我在附近\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Where will you be? - Around.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.53,1:55:02.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 其他人呢？ - 在祷告\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.14,1:55:13.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有天堂吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Do you believe in this heaven shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.68,1:55:15.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.15,1:55:20.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.02,1:55:24.39,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么能相信呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What else have we got to believe in?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.48,1:55:26.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是事实\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ain't that the fuckin' truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.83,1:55:35.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,去它的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What the fuck.
