Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.95,2:08:37.07,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在 - 你呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Now! - What about you?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.16,2:08:40.33,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要留下 - 这里会灌进十顿热铅\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm staying. - There'll be ten tons of hot lead in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:40.41,2:08:43.16,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我说过 我想死 - 我们说好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm telling you, I wanna die! - We got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.25,2:08:46.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗？ 它先死 然后才是你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Remember? It dies first, then you!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.08,2:08:48.92,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你不走我也不走 快走吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm not gonna move without you. Now get going!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.24,2:09:07.51,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 迪伦 - 我在这儿挡住它\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Dillon? - I've gotta hold it here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.56,2:09:10.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那我呢？ - 上帝会照顾你 妹子\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- What about me? - God will take care of you, sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.32,2:09:12.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.61,2:09:14.52,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把热铅倒下来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pour the lead.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.83,2:09:23.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Now, fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.12,2:09:29.54,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 - 快倒 蕾普莉 快呀\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- No! - Go on, Ripley. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.71,2:09:35.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把铅倒下来 快点\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pour the lead, Ripley. Pour it now!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.26,2:09:38.79,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你只有这点能耐？来呀 浑蛋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Come on! Is that all you got? Fight, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.89,2:09:42.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点 倒呀 - 莫斯 这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Come on, do it! - Morse, over here!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.23,2:09:47.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 蕾普莉 - 把铅倒下去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Ripley! - Pour the lead!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.02,2:09:50.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,把铅倒下去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pour the lead!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.48,2:09:52.56,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,倒下去\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Pour it!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.50,2:10:49.91,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌虫子了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I hate bugs!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.65,2:11:19.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾普莉 它热得滚烫\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ripley! It's burning hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.53,2:11:21.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,打开洒水器\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Hit the sprinkler!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.08,2:11:25.15,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,淋死这王八蛋\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Douse the fucker!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.11,2:12:00.74,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.82,2:12:03.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.64,2:13:11.17,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不要再过来 - 等等 他们是来帮忙\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Don't come any closer. - Wait! They're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.27,2:13:12.81,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.06,2:13:18.44,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 蕾普利 - 主教\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Ripley. - Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.32,2:13:21.85,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是来帮助你的 - 别再骗我了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- I'm here to help you. - No more bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.07,2:13:24.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,它在我体内蠕动\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I just felt it move.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.57,2:13:27.61,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道我是谁吗？ - 你是个生化人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You know who I am? - You're a droid.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.70,2:13:30.99,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,与主教同型号 公司派来的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Same model as Bishop. Sent by the fucking company.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.08,2:13:35.12,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是主教那种生化人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No. I'm not the Bishop android.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.21,2:13:37.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我设计的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I designed it.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.54,2:13:42.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是人类 公司派个熟悉面孔来找你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm very human. The company sent me here to show you a friendly face.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.51,2:13:46.42,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,表示你有多重要\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}To demonstrate how important you are to us.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.51,2:13:47.97,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,对我也是\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}To me.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.05,2:13:51.30,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你只想把它带回去 - 我们要杀了它 带你回家\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You wanna take it back. - We want to kill it and take you home.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.39,2:13:52.50,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.60,2:13:55.89,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 我们想帮你\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're wrong. We want to help.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.98,2:13:57.22,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.37,2:14:02.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们会替你取出它 - 然后留它活口\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- We're gonna take that out of you. - And keep it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.40,2:14:07.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让它活着 否则人类将面临危机\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We can't let it live. Everything would be in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.82,2:14:13.57,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不想把它带回去？ - 蕾普莉 时间不多\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- You don't want to take it back? - Ripley, time is important.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.61,2:14:17.62,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要赶快解决这个恶魔\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let us deal with the malignancy.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:17.70,2:14:23.04,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,救援舰有手术台 跟我来吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}We've got a surgical bay set up on the rescue ship. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.00,2:14:26.41,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,手术快速无痛\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's very quick. Painless.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.25,2:14:31.63,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,只要几刀 两小时就好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}A couple of incisions. You'll be out for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.17,2:14:35.25,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就结束了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And then it's over.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.68,2:14:43.09,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你还能过正常生活\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You still can have a life.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.69,2:14:45.72,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,生儿育女\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Children.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.44,2:14:50.48,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 你会知道它真正死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}And most important, you'll know it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.57,2:14:52.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,让我帮你吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.03,2:14:56.86,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样肯定\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What guarantee do I have,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.16,2:15:00.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你们把它取出来\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}once you've taken it out,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.58,2:15:04.03,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,就会消灭它？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}that you'll destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.12,2:15:07.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你得相信我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.96,2:15:14.00,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,求你相信我\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Please? Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.47,2:15:19.67,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.86,2:15:32.35,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这样有什么用？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What's this gonna achieve?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.15,2:15:34.40,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.20,2:15:37.27,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Oh, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.20,2:15:41.28,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Morse.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.16,2:15:46.32,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你愿意帮助我吗？ - 你要我做什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Will you help me? - What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.21,2:15:52.88,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个误会 你们不该伤人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It was a mistake. There was no need for any of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:52.96,2:15:54.29,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的生化人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Fuckin' android!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.02,2:16:15.60,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是生化人\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I'm not a droid!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.61,2:16:19.94,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾普莉\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Ripley!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.03,2:16:22.90,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,想想能从它身上学到的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Think of all we could learn from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.99,2:16:26.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,这是毕生难逢的机会\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}It's the chance of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.20,2:16:30.45,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你得让我留下它 它是个优秀生物\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You must let me have it. It's a magnificent specimen.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.26,2:16:38.08,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拍摄\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No pictures!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:06.70,2:17:08.95,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:09.87,2:17:11.75,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.22,2:17:22.59,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}No!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.66,2:18:25.53,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点 快点走 - 去你的\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}- Come on, you. Get going! - Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.51,2:18:36.80,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,…艾许和达拉斯船长 都死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}...Ash and Captain Dallas are dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.89,2:18:39.34,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,货物和船全部被毁\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}Cargo and ship destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.76,2:18:44.38,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我在六周后将抵达边界\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}I should reach the frontier in about six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.48,2:18:48.31,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的话 有人会来拯救\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}With a bit of luck, the network will pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.40,2:18:52.64,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,我是蕾普莉 诺斯都罗莫号唯一生还者\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}This is Ripley, last survivor of the Nostromo,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:53.74,2:18:55.11,硬字幕4,,0000,0000,0000,,报告完毕\N{\fnTahoma\fs42\1c&HCEE7FF&}signing off.
